data.title: Ashton Kutcher and Mila Kunis marry in secret wedding: report
data.meta_description: That '70s Show actors Ashton Kutcher and Mila Kunis got married this weekend in secret wedding in California, People magazine reports.
data.text:
Actors Ashton Kutcher and Mila Kunis reportedly made it official this weekend, tying the knot in a small ceremony on Sunday, People magazine reports.

The nuptials reportedly took place at The Secret Garden at Parrish Ranch in Oak Glen, Calif., a fittingly secluded setting for the notoriously private couple.

Kutcher, 37, and Kunis, 31, originally met while filming the sitcom That '70s Show, which ran on Fox from 1998 to 2006.

But the pair didn't start dating until 2012 and became engaged in 2014.

Ashton Kutcher gives Winnipeg man nod for romantic video

The pair welcomed a baby girl, named Wyatt, in October.

The marriage is Kunis's first and Kutcher's second.

Kutcher was married to Ghost star Demi Moore from 2005 to 2013.
